{"id":231863566,"title":"辦公室風雲","content":"討論#無雷\nhttps://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYX.jpg\n本人非常非常喜歡情境喜劇，被一位美國朋友推薦了這部，好稱美國人都愛看部？！台灣好像比較少人知道，主題就是一間辦公室發生的種種趣事，但是！我撐到第二季前就撐不下去了，至於為啥呢？我先講講這部特別的地方。\n\n他是採用單機，紀錄片的形式拍攝，大部分的情境喜劇都是多機的，所以在鏡位，情緒，剪輯上能快速切換，達到笑點不斷，這也是我不太適應這部的地方，單機加上紀錄片的拍法，速度放慢很多，笑點也來的較慢，看我看的有點無聊，哈哈，但是還是有很多人愛看這部，可以分享一下觀影心得嗎？哈哈","excerpt":"討論#無雷，本人非常非常喜歡情境喜劇，被一位美國朋友推薦了這部，好稱美國人都愛看部？！台灣好像比較少人知道，主題就是一間辦公室發生的種種趣事，但是！我撐到第二季前就撐不下去了，至於為啥呢？我先講講這部","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"28e79ba0-8ded-4acc-a6b2-f015bdef7605","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-15T05:10:01.252Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-15T05:10:01.252Z","commentCount":11,"likeCount":22,"tags":[],"topics":["歐美影集板"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"歐美影集","forumAlias":"ea_series","school":"輔仁大學","department":"織品服裝學系 服飾設計組","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":21},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYX.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"78106b59-231c-4142-9586-58d3cdd06184","url":"https://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYXl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYXl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYXl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-15T05:10:01.252Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-15T05:10:01.252Z"},{"id":"78106b59-231c-4142-9586-58d3cdd06184","url":"https://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYX.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/1XvGUYX","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/1XvGUYXl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-15T05:10:01.252Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-15T05:10:01.252Z"}],"postAvatar":""}